  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003ELaserTherapyU interviews Thomas Mang PhD, Research Professor-University of Buffalo at the SPIE-Photonics West Conference in San Francisco February 2016 for his views on his presentation and research into TBI and the effects of photobiomodulation on the cell astrocyte, and where low level laser research is headed in the future.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cbr /\u003E"
}]]></Value>
